portantly=E2=80=A6
* Instacart has infinite capacity to bring more advertisers on the app whic=
h means=E2=80=A6
* Instacart can massively increase profitability by adding more advertisers=
 to its auction-based model; more liquidity means higher prices.

Now that is a tech company.

